title: (Thurs Full Show) It's Morgan2's Birthday + Lunchbox's Business Pitch To Barbara Corcoran + Bobby Feud: Top 10 Most Good Looking Guys In Country Music
itunes:title: (Thurs Full Show) It's Morgan2's Birthday + Lunchbox's Business Pitch To Barbara Corcoran + Bobby Feud: Top 10 Most Good Looking Guys In Country Music
description:
We celebrate Morgan2's birthday on the show! Plus, Shark Tank's Barbara Corcoran is on the show tomorrow and Lunchbox thinks he has a genius business idea he wants to pitch to her. We share our thoughts on it. Then, we play the Bobby Feud! We try to name the Top 10 most good looking guys in country music! Find out who the top answer is and who guessed it right!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
